                            <comment id="140350" author="lixi" created="Thu, 28 Jan 2016 15:11:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;With the --no-initramfs, installing/uninstalling luster-module RPM speeds up a lot:&lt;br/&gt;
RPM Install Uninstall&lt;br/&gt;
--no-initramfs 6.852s 4.867s&lt;br/&gt;
Origin 2m48.694s 2m6.769s&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
